      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>pork mince </strong>(remove the paper if required!) and <strong>chopped garlic & ginger </strong>in a bowl with <strong>half </strong>your <strong>soy sauce </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up until thoroughly combined (clean hands is the best way!)</p><p>Divide and shape into 1 equal-sized patty per person</p>",
