      "instruction": "<p>While the patties are cooking, chop your <strong>coriander</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Slice your <strong>red chilli[es]</strong> finely</p><p>Combine your <strong>rice vinegar</strong>, <strong>remaining soy sauce </strong>and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp] </span><strong>sugar </strong>in a large bowl</p><p>Add your <strong>mooli slaw mix</strong>, <strong>chopped coriander </strong>and <strong>chilli rounds </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the bowl and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>zingy slaw</strong></p>",
